- F3 is structurally redundant across the standard four-form battery.
- F4's microscope sensitivity scales with the fixture's binade dynamic range near singularity.

This is a 1-page methodology note worth writing — not the full evolution-doc, but a clarification of what the four-form battery actually measures across fixtures.

